summary: Hey @taylorswift , today was my sister's baby shower! One of the activities I organized was decorating onesies for the baby......
body:
Hey @taylorswift , today was my sister’s baby shower! One of the activities I organized was decorating onesies for the baby… what do you think of my creation?

My sister and I used to blast “You belong with me” in the car when she would drive us home. If we had had a bad day we would wind the windows all the way down and do a few extra laps of the block, SCREAMING it at the top of our lungs. It was the best time we had together! I can’t wait to teach my new little niece the same joy!

summary: Just for fun i thought i wonder if there is a butterfly with her name and found this. "Euphydryad editha taylori, the Whulge...
question: Just for fun i thought i wonder if there is a butterfly with her name and found this. "Euphydryad editha taylori, the Whulge checkerspot or Taylor's checkerspot, is a butterfly native to an area of the northwestern United States and Vancouver Island" it looks similar to the snake cocoon butterfly you found.
answer:
okay anon this is beautiful

first off, this butterfly is native to where i grew up as a kid and so i didn’t even think of it! they’re so pretty..

also, grab a cup of cocoa and sit down for nine minutes of wholesome with this short news story on how the women of an all women’s prison have been working to save this butterfly from extinction. oh. my. goodness.
